Ed the monk, Fred the SK, Zed the ranger, and Ned the bard all want a CoF. Raid leader (or loot distributor) then assigns numbers and announces...<br>
Ed is 0, 1 and 2, Fred is 3 and 4, Zed is 5 and 6, Ned is 7<br>
